---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="convenience" channelName="convenience" channelColor="#A14D7C">
<style>
.ch-header{padding:28px 0 20px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(161,77,124,.2);margin-bottom:24px}
.ch-label{font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(161,77,124,.7);margin-bottom:6px}
.ch-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#A14D7C;line-height:1.2}
.ch-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:#7A9AB5;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.6}
.brand-tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.brand-tab{padding:5px 12px;border:1px solid rgba(161,77,124,.3);border-radius:100px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;color:rgba(161,77,124,.7);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.brand-tab.active,.brand-tab:hover{background:rgba(161,77,124,.15);border-color:#A14D7C;color:#A14D7C}
.combo-card{border:1px solid rgba(161,77,124,.2);border-radius:3px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:10px;background:rgba(161,77,124,.03)}
.combo-brand{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(161,77,124,.6);margin-bottom:5px}
.combo-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#FBF9F4;margin-bottom:5px}
.combo-items{font-size:12px;color:#7A9AB5;line-height:1.7}
.cta-box{border:1px solid #5B0E1B;border-radius:3px;padding:20px 16px;margin-top:28px;text-align:center;background:rgba(91,14,27,.08)}
.cta-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}
.cta-desc{font-size:12px;color:#7A9AB5;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.6}
.cta-btn{display:block;padding:13px;background:#5B0E1B;border-radius:2px;color:#FBF9F4;font-family:'League Spartan',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none}
</style>

<div class="ch-header">
  <div class="ch-label">taerijay+ · 24h convenience</div>
  <div class="ch-title">convenience</div>
  <div class="ch-desc">24시 편의점 PB 꿀조합 가이드 — 🌐 GS25 · CU · 세븐일레븐 브랜드별 비교 DB</div>
</div>

<div class="brand-tabs">
  <button class="brand-tab active">ALL</button>
  <button class="brand-tab">GS25</button>
  <button class="brand-tab">CU</button>
  <button class="brand-tab">7-ELEVEN</button>
</div>

<div class="combo-card">
  <div class="combo-brand">GS25 · 편의점 꿀조합</div>
  <div class="combo-name">GS25 혜자로운 한 끼 조합</div>
  <div class="combo-items">혜자로운 도시락 + 오징어땅콩 + 레쓰비<br>💡 총 4,200원 · 한국 직장인 점심 대표 조합 확인됨.</div>
</div>
<div class="combo-card">
  <div class="combo-brand">CU · 편의점 꿀조합</div>
  <div class="combo-name">CU HEYROO 인기 야식 조합</div>
  <div class="combo-items">즉석 라면 (컵라면) + 삼각김밥 2개 + 바나나우유<br>💡 총 3,800원 · 야간 편의점 1위 조합 인증됨.</div>
</div>
<div class="combo-card">
  <div class="combo-brand">7-ELEVEN · 편의점 꿀조합</div>
  <div class="combo-name">세븐일레븐 도보여행자 조합</div>
  <div class="combo-items">샌드위치 + 아메리카노 (500ml) + 에너지바<br>💡 총 4,500원 · 장거리 이동 여행자 추천 조합임.</div>
</div>
<div class="combo-card">
  <div class="combo-brand">GS25 · PB 단독 추천</div>
  <div class="combo-name">유어스 PB 뷰티 편의점 세트</div>
  <div class="combo-items">유어스 선크림 SPF50+ + 리무버 패드<br>💡 다이소 대비 접근성 1위 · 24시 구매 가능함.</div>
</div>

<div class="cta-box">
  <div class="cta-title">전체 편의점 꿀조합 DB</div>
  <div class="cta-desc">GS25·CU·세븐일레븐·이마트24 전 브랜드 PB 비교 + 지역별 야경 편의점 위치 DB는 구독자 전용임.</div>
  <a href="/02-payment/payment?key=cvs_basic" class="cta-btn">convenience Basic 구독 — $19.99 →</a>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  if (!sessionStorage.getItem('user_email')) {
    window.location.href = '/01-auth/auth?redirect=' + encodeURIComponent(window.location.href);
  }
</script>
</Layout>